title: Enums for Level 1 feed System commands. See Level 1 Port System Messages

javaEnums.title: Disables the once per second timestamp.
Timestamps default to on, but in the event you have stopped them manually, this will restart them into the stream.
Enable Regional Quotes ("R" messages) for the symbol specified.
Disable Regional Quotes ("R" messages) for the symbol specified.
Enable Streaming News ("N" messages) to be received for all news sources authorized.
Disable Streaming News ("N" messages) from being received.
Request a S,CURRENT UPDATE FIELDNAMES,Symbol,... message,.
Request to change the current update/summary message fieldset. Please see Dynamic Fieldsets for more info.
Request to change the current level of logging in IQConnect. Please see IQConnect Logging for more info.
Request to unwatch all Level 1 symbols that are currently being watched.
Tells the feed to initiate a connection to the servers.
Tells the feed to disconnect from the servers.
